FIELD.name: collection
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: data collection this observation belongs to

FIELD.name: collectionID
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: collection-specific unique observation identifier

FIELD.name: instrument_name
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: name of the instrument used to collect the data

FIELD.name: position_center_ra
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: RA of central coordinates

FIELD.name: position_center_dec
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: DEC of central coordinates

FIELD.name: position_naxes
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: number of axes

FIELD.name: position_naxis
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: dimensions (number of pixels) along spatial axes

FIELD.name: position_scale
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: pixel size along spatial axes

FIELD.name: position_bounds
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: spatial bounds of the data

FIELD.name: energy_bounds_center
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: medianvalue on energy axis (barycentric wavelength)

FIELD.name: energy_bounds_cval1
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: lower bound on energy axis (barycentric wavelength)

FIELD.name: energy_bounds_cval2
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: upper bound on energy axis (barycentric wavelength)

FIELD.name: energy_units
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: units used for energy values

FIELD.name: energy_bandpassName
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: collection-specific name for energy band (e.g. filter name)

FIELD.name: time_bounds_center
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: central value on time axis (Modified Julian Day)

FIELD.name: time_bounds_cval1
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: lower bound on time axis (Modified Julian Day)

FIELD.name: time_bounds_cval2
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: upper bound on time axis (Modified Julian Day)

FIELD.name: time_exposure
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: actual exposure time

FIELD.name: imageFormat
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: mimetype of the data file(s)

FIELD.name: accessURL
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: data access URL

FIELD.name: metaRelease
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: UTC timestamp when metadata is publicly visible

FIELD.name: dataRelease
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: UTC timestamp when data is publicly available
